    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if there is no \"beneath the mask\"? what if the mask is all that's left? it's like i'm just a hollow shell, just an empty container. i'm tired of holding up this pretend life when the person who was supposed to live it is already dead. it feels like i'm just waiting for the world to realize i'm not actually here.",
